title: Grateful Dead Live at Cal Expo on 1991-08-14
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Little Red Rooster, Loser, Black Throated Wind, Row Jimmy, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Cold Rain & Snow, Box Of Rain, Looks Like Rain, Crazy Fingers-> Estimated Prophet-> Supplication Jam-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Walkin' Blues-> Around & Around, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

reviews.review_text:
Jerry's vocals buried in mix.  WTF Healey? Too busy doing lines at the board to realize Jerry's vocals are half as loud as Bob's all night? 

Frustrating listen. Caliope sound with too many keyboards. (And I am a keyboardist.) 

Turned off before Drums.
